{
	"name": "The Flame Remember",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-eye.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 14th level, the ability you choose as a spellcasting ability is increased by 2 and you can go up to 22 in this ability instead of 20.</p><p>Whenever you use a spell of the <em>knowledge</em> school, the information you receive are more accurate, and you gain an expertise die on a skill of your choice until your next long rest. While you are within 30 feet of any natural fire, you may cast @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.kbyg7uvh3w8osgiq]{Sending} or speak aloud through any other fire within 1 mile as if using message. You don’t need to know the location of the other fire—your patron knows, and routes the message accordingly.</p><p>When you light a flame somewhere, you can see through this flame what happened here in the last hundred years, as if your vision was directly projected into the past. You can give a date and an hour if you want to see specific things.</p><p>You can use this feature only once per Long Rest.</p>",
